                     <interp inst="t17880625-52-off231" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17880625-52-cd232" type="crimeDate">18th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880625-52-off231 t17880625-52-cd232"></join>, two pair of plated shoe buckles, value 6 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880625-52-victim446" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Clarke
                  <interp inst="t17880625-52-victim446" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880625-52-victim446" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
